title: Instructions: Preheat oven to 425ยบ. Press crust into a 9 inch pan, prick crust and bake until lightly browned, about 10 minutes. Whisk together the eggs, milk, salt and pepper. Sprinkle the bacon, sausage, ham, green onions, and cheese evenly on top of precooked crust. Pour the egg mixture on top and bake for 20 minutes until the center is set. Allow to cool slightly before serving.
